the difference between JMeter and HP LoadRunner? Jmeter is an open source tool that has a limited protocol support, while HP LoadRunner is not open source that supports more protocols.
not one of the components of HP LoadRunner? Sampler.

Visual user generator? it generates virtual users as its name says (file -> new script)
Scripts in Vugen are written in C language.
the actions in the Vugen scripts? vuser_init , Action, and vuser_end.
LoadRunner Controller is used to control the virtual users and record the test results.
